<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Créez une adresse email temporaire gratuite, anonyme et instantanée.">
    <title>SelfMail — Temp mail</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/logo.png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/logo.png">
    <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>

    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: #f0f4f8;
            color: #1a2035;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }

        header {
            background: #1a2035;
            padding: 0 32px;
            height: 56px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .header-logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 9px;
        }

        .header-logo-icon {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0cc9a4, #08a88a);
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .header-logo-icon svg {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .header-logo-name {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #fff;
            letter-spacing: -0.2px;
        }

        .header-right {
            font-size: .75rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,.4);
        }

        .hero {
            background: #1a2035;
            padding: 48px 20px 56px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: 1.35rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            letter-spacing: -.2px;
        }

        .hero-email-wrap {
            max-width: 560px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 6px 6px 6px 20px;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        #email-display {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 0;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #fff;
            letter-spacing: .2px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            outline: none;
            font-family: 'Poppins', monospace;
        }

        .hero-copy-btn {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0cc9a4, #08a88a);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 9px;
            padding: 10px 22px;
            font-size: .85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 7px;
            transition: filter .18s, transform .15s;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        .hero-copy-btn:hover { filter: brightness(1.1); }
        .hero-copy-btn:active { transform: scale(.96); }
        .hero-copy-btn svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; overflow: visible; }

        .hero-sub {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 20px auto 0;
            font-size: .8rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,.35);
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .hero-timer {
            margin-top: 14px;
            font-size: .78rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,.3);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .hero-timer svg { width: 13px; height: 13px; }

        #timer-display {
            color: #f5b942;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        #timer-display.danger { color: #f87171; }

        #conn-wrap {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 5px;
            margin-left: 16px;
        }

        #conn-dot {
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #f5b942;
        }

        #conn-dot.on  { background: #0cc9a4; }
        #conn-dot.off { background: #f87171; }

        #conn-label { color: rgba(255,255,255,.3); }

        .actions-section {
            background: #f0f4f8;
            padding: 28px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .actions-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            justify-content: center;
            max-width: 480px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .action-btn {
            flex: 1 1 calc(50% - 6px);
            min-width: 180px;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 13px 20px;
            font-size: .85rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #374151;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 9px;
            transition: all .18s;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        .action-btn svg { width: 17px; height: 17px; overflow: visible; }
        .action-btn:hover { background: #f8fafd; border-color: #c7d2e0; box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.09); transform: translateY(-1px); }
        .action-btn:active { transform: translateY(0) scale(.97); }

        .action-btn.copy-btn  { color: #0cc9a4; border-color: rgba(12,201,164,.25); }
        .action-btn.copy-btn:hover { background: rgba(12,201,164,.05); }
        .action-btn.del-btn   { color: #ef4444; border-color: rgba(239,68,68,.2); }
        .action-btn.del-btn:hover { background: rgba(239,68,68,.04); }

        .main {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px 60px;
        }

        .inbox-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.07);
        }

        .inbox-header {
            background: #1a2035;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 3fr 90px;
            padding: 14px 24px;
        }

        .inbox-header span {
            font-size: .7rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.2px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,.5);
        }

        #empty-state {
            padding: 72px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .empty-icon {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            background: #f0f4f8;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
        }

        .empty-icon svg { width: 26px; height: 26px; color: #94a3b8; }

        .empty-title {
            font-size: .95rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .empty-sub {
            font-size: .8rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }

        #email-list {
            display: none;
        }

        .email-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 3fr 90px;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 15px 24px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background .14s;
            animation: rowIn .3s ease;
        }

        @keyframes rowIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-6px); }
            to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .email-row:hover { background: #f8fafd; }
        .email-row.active { background: #f0faf8; }
        .email-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

        .email-row.unread .row-subject { font-weight: 600; color: #1a2035; }

        .row-sender, .row-subject {
            font-size: .84rem;
            color: #374151;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            padding-right: 12px;
        }

        .row-sender { color: #64748b; }

        .row-unread-dot {
            display: none;
            width: 7px;
            height: 7px;
            background: #0cc9a4;
            border-radius: 50%;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .email-row.unread .row-unread-dot { display: inline-block; }

        .row-sender-wrap {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .row-actions {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            justify-content: flex-end;
        }

        .btn-view {
            background: #0cc9a4;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 5px 13px;
            font-size: .75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: filter .15s;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        .btn-view:hover { filter: brightness(1.1); }

        .btn-del-row {
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            color: #cbd5e1;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 4px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: color .15s, background .15s;
        }

        .btn-del-row svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; }
        .btn-del-row:hover { color: #ef4444; background: rgba(239,68,68,.08); }

        .detail-section {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-top: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.07);
            display: none;
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: fadeUp .25s ease;
        }

        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .detail-bar {
            background: #1a2035;
            padding: 14px 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .detail-bar-title {
            font-size: .75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,.5);
        }

        .btn-close-detail {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.08);
            border: none;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,.6);
            padding: 5px 14px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: .75rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            transition: background .15s;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        .btn-close-detail svg { width: 13px; height: 13px; }
        .btn-close-detail:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.14); }

        .detail-meta {
            padding: 20px 24px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
        }

        #detail-subject {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a2035;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .detail-meta-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: .78rem;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .detail-meta-key { color: #94a3b8; width: 40px; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .detail-meta-val { color: #374151; }

        .detail-body {
            padding: 24px;
        }

        #detail-iframe {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 280px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: #fff;
            display: none;
        }

        #detail-text {
            font-size: .85rem;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.8;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            display: none;
        }

        .modal-backdrop {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,.45);
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            transition: opacity .2s;
        }

        .modal-backdrop.open {
            opacity: 1;
            pointer-events: all;
        }

        .modal {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 32px;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
            transform: scale(.94) translateY(8px);
            transition: transform .25s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1);
        }

        .modal-backdrop.open .modal {
            transform: scale(1) translateY(0);
        }

        .modal-title {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a2035;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .modal-desc {
            font-size: .84rem;
            color: #64748b;
            line-height: 1.65;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .modal-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            justify-content: flex-end;
        }

        .btn-modal-cancel {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: .84rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #64748b;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            transition: background .15s;
        }

        .btn-modal-cancel:hover { background: #e2e8f0; }

        .btn-modal-confirm {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0cc9a4, #08a88a);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: .84rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            transition: filter .15s;
        }

        .btn-modal-confirm:hover { filter: brightness(1.08); }

        #toast {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 24px;
            right: 24px;
            z-index: 200;
            background: #1a2035;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            max-width: 300px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,.25);
            transform: translateY(70px);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: transform .3s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1), opacity .25s;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        #toast.show {
            transform: translateY(0);
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .toast-dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background: #0cc9a4;
            border-radius: 50%;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .toast-body { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }

        #toast-subject {
            font-size: .82rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
        }

        #toast-from {
            font-size: .73rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,.5);
            margin-top: 2px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .inbox-header,
            .email-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; }
            .inbox-header span:nth-child(2),
            .row-subject { display: none; }
            .actions-grid { flex-direction: column; }
            .action-btn { min-width: 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="header-logo">
            <img src="/logo.png" alt="SelfMail" style="width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:8px;object-fit:cover;">
            <span class="header-logo-name">SelfMail</span>
        </div>
        <span class="header-right">Email temporaire gratuit</span>
    </header>

    <div class="hero">
        <h1 class="hero-title">Votre adresse email temporaire</h1>
        <div class="hero-email-wrap">
            <span id="email-display">Génération en cours...</span>
            <button class="hero-copy-btn" id="btn-copy">
                <svg id="icon-copy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="overflow:visible">
                    <rect x="9" y="9" width="13" height="13" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                    <path d="M5 15H4a2 2 0 01-2-2V4a2 2 0 012-2h9a2 2 0 012 2v1"/>
                </svg>
                <svg id="icon-check" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="display:none;">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                Copier
            </button>
        </div>
        <p class="hero-sub">Protégez votre vraie adresse. Recevez des emails instantanément, sans inscription. Tout est supprimé automatiquement.</p>
        <div class="hero-timer">
            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
            Expire dans&nbsp;<span id="timer-display">10:00</span>
            <span id="conn-wrap">
                <span id="conn-dot"></span>
                <span id="conn-label">Connexion...</span>
            </span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="actions-section">
        <div class="actions-grid">
            <button class="action-btn copy-btn" id="btn-copy-2">
                <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="overflow:visible">
                    <rect x="9" y="9" width="13" height="13" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                    <path d="M5 15H4a2 2 0 01-2-2V4a2 2 0 012-2h9a2 2 0 012 2v1"/>
                </svg>
                Copier
            </button>
            <button class="action-btn" id="btn-refresh">
                <svg id="icon-refresh" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                          d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/>
                </svg>
                Actualiser
            </button>
            <button class="action-btn" id="btn-new">
                <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                          d="M15.232 5.232l3.536 3.536m-2.036-5.036a2.5 2.5 0 113.536 3.536L6.5 21.036H3v-3.572L16.732 3.732z"/>
                </svg>
                Changer
            </button>
            <button class="action-btn del-btn" id="btn-delete-all">
                <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                          d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/>
                </svg>
                Supprimer tout
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main">
        <div class="inbox-card">
            <div class="inbox-header">
                <span>Expéditeur</span>
                <span>Objet</span>
                <span style="text-align:right;">Action</span>
            </div>

            <div id="empty-state">
                <div class="empty-icon">
                    <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5"
                              d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <p class="empty-title">Votre boîte est vide</p>
                <p class="empty-sub">En attente d'emails entrants…</p>
            </div>

            <div id="email-list"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="detail-section" id="detail-section">
            <div class="detail-bar">
                <span class="detail-bar-title">Contenu du message</span>
                <button class="btn-close-detail" id="btn-close-detail">
                    <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/>
                    </svg>
                    Fermer
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-meta">
                <div id="detail-subject"></div>
                <div class="detail-meta-row">
                    <span class="detail-meta-key">De</span>
                    <span class="detail-meta-val" id="detail-from"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-meta-row">
                    <span class="detail-meta-key">Date</span>
                    <span class="detail-meta-val" id="detail-date"></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-body">
                <iframe id="detail-iframe" sandbox="allow-same-origin"></iframe>
                <pre id="detail-text"></pre>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="modal-new" class="modal-backdrop">
        <div class="modal">
            <p class="modal-title">Changer d'adresse email ?</p>
            <p class="modal-desc">L'adresse actuelle et tous ses emails seront <strong style="color:#ef4444;">supprimés</strong>. Une nouvelle adresse sera générée immédiatement.</p>
            <div class="modal-actions">
                <button class="btn-modal-cancel" id="modal-cancel">Annuler</button>
                <button class="btn-modal-confirm" id="modal-confirm">Changer</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="modal-delete-all" class="modal-backdrop">
        <div class="modal">
            <p class="modal-title">Supprimer tous les emails ?</p>
            <p class="modal-desc">Tous les emails de votre boîte seront <strong style="color:#ef4444;">définitivement supprimés</strong>. Cette action est irréversible.</p>
            <div class="modal-actions">
                <button class="btn-modal-cancel" id="modal-del-cancel">Annuler</button>
                <button class="btn-modal-confirm" id="modal-del-confirm" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ef4444,#dc2626);">Supprimer</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="toast">
        <span class="toast-dot"></span>
        <div class="toast-body">
            <div id="toast-subject">Nouvel email</div>
            <div id="toast-from"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <style>
        @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
        .spinning { animation: spin .7s linear infinite; }
    </style>

    <script>window.MAIL_DOMAIN = '<%= mailDomain %>';</script>
    <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
